name: Cloudstorming
tagline: Cloud Storming - Where technology may learn.
body:
### Current Objectives
We have been striving for optimal math equations & programs to increase math performance for usage within the class files. 
_The math equations have currently benchmark'd performance faster than standard for-loops and operator-based equations_

### Our Goal
The end results is to have a system keep enhancing it's own languages/programs so as to increase performance and provide efficient outputs.

### Usage
Our systems are designed for the `Object Avoidance System`, `Global Addressing System`, and `Wireless Electricity Positioning System`

### Contributors
Project Lead: Caleb Ferguson (@CFerg)
